says your Buliwyf has plans
to take his kingdom.

504
00:45:26,590 --> 00:45:29,650
- [ Chuckles ]
- Is there truth in this ?

505
00:45:29,760 --> 00:45:32,058
No.

506
00:45:37,034 --> 00:45:38,899
You may believe me.

507
00:45:40,671 --> 00:45:43,231
Then be cautious.

508
00:45:50,647 --> 00:45:53,207
- She would say no more.
- [ Scoffs ]

509
00:45:53,317 --> 00:45:55,444
She doesn't need to.

510
00:45:55,552 --> 00:45:58,316
Prince, aah !
[ Spits ]

511
00:46:05,395 --> 00:46:07,295
<i>[ Buliwyf ] We'll need an example.</i>

512
00:46:09,967 --> 00:46:12,026
<i>[ Man ] The redhead?</i>

513
00:46:12,169 --> 00:46:13,796
Mm-hmm.

514
00:46:13,937 --> 00:46:16,770
I'll do it.

515
00:46:16,874 --> 00:46:19,274
You shouldn't be involved.

516
00:46:21,845 --> 00:46:25,906
- What should I do ?
- Keep your teeth together
and go back to work.

