519
00:46:57,447 --> 00:46:59,347
You dig like a dog.

520
00:47:02,052 --> 00:47:04,043
Did you call me a dog ?

521
00:47:04,154 --> 00:47:08,056
I said you dig like one, flinging
earth carelessly like an animal.

522
00:47:08,158 --> 00:47:11,286
So, now
I'm an animal ?

523
00:47:11,395 --> 00:47:13,226
You're not listening.

524
00:47:13,330 --> 00:47:15,264
I'm deaf?

525
00:47:15,365 --> 00:47:17,265
You're a fool,
little man.

526
00:47:17,401 --> 00:47:21,235
That is because, <i>boy,</i>
your words are feeble...

527
00:47:21,338 --> 00:47:23,738
and twisted
as an old woman's !

528
00:47:23,841 --> 00:47:26,639
This old woman'll send you
to the next world, old man !

529
00:47:26,877 --> 00:47:29,744
<i>[ Crowd Murmuring ]</i>

530
00:47:31,415 --> 00:47:33,315
- What happened ?
-<i>[ Metal Scraping ]</i>

531
00:47:33,417 --> 00:47:36,750
An engineering dispute.
[ Chuckles ]

532
00:47:38,188 --> 00:47:39,951
<i>[ Scraping Continues ]</i>

533
00:47:43,827 --> 00:47:46,990
- You notice he's bigger than you ?
- <i>Yes.</i>

534
00:47:47,097 --> 00:47:50,191
- And younger ?
- Yes.

535
00:47:52,569 --> 00:47:56,130
- Bet on him, if you like.
- I may !

536
00:47:56,273 --> 00:47:58,173
[ Both Grunting ]

537
00:48:06,550 --> 00:48:09,348
Luck.

538
00:48:09,453 --> 00:48:12,149
[ Crowd Murmuring ]

539
00:48:21,899 --> 00:48:24,197
[ Both Grunting ]

540
00:48:27,804 --> 00:48:29,704
Aah !

541
00:48:33,277 --> 00:48:35,837
